BTCData,monitors,and,records,all,Bitcoin,transactions,and,public,payment,addresses,used,in,transactions,Developers,can,retrieve,information,and,statistics,on,Bitcoin,transactions,programmatically,using,the,RESTful,BTCData,API,This,can,be,used,to,get,information,on,whether,a,transaction,has,confirmed,whether,someone,has,sent,the,user,a,payment,recently,the,total,amount,of,Bitcoins,paid,to,a,given,address,and,more